name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Hospital or Convalescent Ratings: Some conditions require periods of hospitalization or constant medical care (at-home nurse, etc.). Any condition that requires this is rated 100% during this intensive treatment.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Accurate Measurements: It is essential that the necessary information to rate your condition is recorded by the physician in your exam. With the information on this page, you should know what needs to be measured and recorded.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: A Tie Goes to the Veteran: If there are two equally strong exams with conflicting information, or if the condition can be equally rated under two different codes, then the one that gives the highest rating will be assigned.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Pyramiding: A single condition can only be rated once! However, if another condition exists that is additional to the skin condition (not simply caused by it), then it can also be rated.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Code 7822: Any other skin conditions that cause hard, scaly bumps (â€œpapulosquamous disordersâ€) to form on the skin that are not listed anywhere else on this page are rated under this code, including mycosis fungoides, lichen planus, plaque parapsoriasi, PLEVA, PRP,

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Code 7818: All other malignant cancers of the skin are rated under this code. If it is active and requires intensive, invasive treatments like chemotherapy, extensive surgery (not just removal from the superficial skin), or x-ray therapy, it is rated 100%

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Code 7833: Malignant melanoma is the most dangerous form of skin cancer. It causes dark patches to form on the skin and can also form in areas inside the body, including the eyes and bowels.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Code 7819: Benign tumors affecting the skin are rated either on scars/disfigurement or on how they affect the functioning of a body part. For example, if the condition interferes with the movement of the elbow, then it would be rated under the limitation of motion of the elbow.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Code 7832: Hyperhidrosis is a condition where the body produces excessive amounts of sweat, even at rest. If the condition is severe enough that you are unable to handle tools or paper because of too much moisture on the hands and it doesnâ€™t respond to treatment, it is rated 30%.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Code 7831: Alopecia areata is a condition where there are circular patches of hair loss all over the body (including the head). If all the hair on the entire body is lost, it is rated 10%. If there is only hair loss on the head, it is rated 0%.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Code 7830: Scarring alopecia is a condition where the hair follicles on the head are replaced by scar tissue, causing permanent hair loss and scarring. If it affects more than 40% of the scalp, it is rated 20%. If it affects 20% to 40% of the scalp, it is rated 10%.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Code 7824: Diseases of keratinization affect the process where the lower layers of the skin turn into the harder outer layer of skin. Keratin is the protein that causes the skin to harden. Any condition that affects the process of keratinization is rated under this code.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Code 7821: Cutaneous manifestations of collagen-vascular diseases are skin conditions that occur when the immune system attacks the collagen. Collagen is the protein that are in the skin. Psoriasis is considered a collagen-vascular disease.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Code 7816: Psoriasis is an autoimmune condition that tells the body to produce more skin cells even though they are not needed. This can cause numerous different things to happen to the skin, including redness, swelling, scaly texture, patches of red bumps, and more.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Code 7815: Bullous disorders cause blisters of clear liquid to form in between the layers of the skin, most often on the inner thighs and upper arms.

name: ğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸Veteran HankğŸ‡ºğŸ‡¸
tweet: Code 7809: Lupus is a condition where the immune system attacks the healthy cells of the skin, causing severe sores, tearing, and scarring of the skin. Most often, these occur on the head near the ears, eyes, nose, lips, and cheeks.

tweet: Cubital tunnel is a condition where the ulnar nerve gets pinched as it passes through the elbow into the forearm. It is rated under the codes for the ulnar nerve.

tweet: Probative Value: If two exams record the condition differently, the exam with the most thorough data and performed by the most qualified person in that specialty will be the exam the rating is based on.

tweet: A Tie Goes to the Veteran: If there are two equally strong exams with conflicting information, or if the condition can be equally rated under two different codes, then the one that gives the highest rating will be assigned in favor of the higher rating.
